data.description: Charming home near downtown Commerce. The home has four bedrooms and 2 bath with a large living room. Kitchen is open galley style and comes with the appliances. Dishwasher and stove are new. Primary bedroom has small sitting area which leads to the primary bath. Bathroom has 2 closets plus a linen closet. Home has a new heating and air system and nice neutral paint throughout. The location is fantastic with a short ride to 441, 15 or 98 making it an easy commute to Athens, Jefferson or Atlanta. Come check out this beautiful home today.
